features: 【1200 Times Recycle】-HENREEPOW rechargeable AA batteries have passed FCC and CE certification，AA rechargeable battery has excellent grade A+ cell for long time use, more than 1200 times recycle full charge-discharge cycles, long-lasting durability and low self-consumption. AA lithium-ion rechargeable batteries save more money than regular batteries. 【Tips: Can't recharged in regular charger. Only for recharged with 4 in 1 USB cable included.】

【High Capacity】-With large capacity 2600mWh, HENREEPOW AA Lithium ion rechargeable batteries can last at least 20% longer time than any other AA batteries, Lithium Batteries are rechargeable and reusable. All HENREEPOW rechargeable batteries have been charged before packing, ready to be used once received.

【Constant 1.5V Output】-HENREEPOW lithium ion batteries,embedded with innovative technology.Each battery is strictly verified at the time of production to ensure that it meets the qualified standards before leaving the factory. The built-in protection chip can effectively avoid the danger of the battery when it is overcharged, overheated or short-circuited.Ideal for digital cameras, game controllers, wireless mouse, toy guns,flashlight, door lock and more for high current applications.

【Quick Charging】-HENREEPOW rechargeable lithium ion aa batteries with 4-in-1 USB charging cable for fully charge in around 1.5 hours. You can charge 4 packs lithium ion AA batteries at the same time. LED indicator shows charging status. Low self-discharge technology make the battery maintain a high capacity state for a long time even without using , multi-protection to make the battery safe assured.

【Easy to Store】-HENREEPOW double A lithium ion rechargeable batteries are neatly packed in a transparent storage box. The battery box is exquisite, beautiful and practical, and will not bring you unnecessary trouble due to dispersion. Note: Please charge fully before use, as we only charge the batteries to 20% for shipping safety purpose. Batteries will reach top performance after 3-5 times fully charge cycles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Doesn't work for Blink doorbell cameras
reviews.reviewText: I got these rechargeable lithium batteries for my Blink doorbell camera, but they don't work for it. I thought maybe they were defective. I charged them fully and they don't work. So I tried them in other electronics and they work. So I guess if u plan on buying these for that particular doorbell camera, don't use these. But they will work for everything else. That's why I took a star off. They work, but they don't serve the purpose that I purchased them for. I guess they'll just be used for my oculus controllers 🤷🏽‍♂️

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Buying more for sure!
reviews.reviewText: I've purchased other brands in the past and while yes they work... they don't work the same. I use these for everything from my photography gear to remote batteries. I've been annoyed by the other brand I bought because they seem to pulse the power. In my coffee whip (or anything with a motor) the other brand doesn't supply a constant flow of power, instead you can hear and see the motor pulsing fast. With these there is no pulsing. They supply a constant and even flow of power. They also seem to hold and supply a charge much longer. At roughly fifty cents more I definitely got more for my money. I'm buying a few more packs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Got hot, melted the little white part on the top button
reviews.reviewText: Bought May 2023, charged and installed in my outdoor blink cameras in June. One outdoor camera is still working on the same battery charge, the second is triggered more often and I had to change the batteries last week. I went to charge the batteries using the supplied cord, the next morning the cabinet I charged items in was warm inside. The MAINS to USB charger itself was HOT (typical wall wart for charging), and the battery was HOT! I immediately unplugged and let cool down. Beware when you charge these. I tried to get assistance from the seller to see about a replacement, however Amazon did not allow me to get assistance for this product beyond boiler items, no returns available.
